{"tid":1674380,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"解散警隊之後  要 行任期制!!!   五年任期!!!","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:17.000Z","uid":262522,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"53cf26017abe5d402fcdbb1d17e418eea7973784","tid":1674380,"uid":262522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"解散警隊之後  要<br />\n行  任期制 !!!<br />\n只可做五年 不可連任<br />\n五年任期後要重返私人市場!!<br />\n<br />\n任期制係民主制度入面一個超有用嘅位!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%2588%25B6&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=946a0e31\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%B6</a><br />\n訂出其行使職權的時限，時限到期職權即刻喪失，以防止官員長期尸位素餐，獨佔公權力。<br />\n<br />\n加泰集會後感想:<br />\n1. PoPo 仆街全球一L樣<br />\n2. 咁仆街其中一個原因其實係終身制, 全球一L樣<br />\n3. 加泰人都只係比西班牙警察打, 可以話係外人, 香港人係比香港警察打, 班仆街反骨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dca331e01d044cbc08e736abedf102bcea1c500","tid":1674380,"uid":122134,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"不如18歲就一定要做5年啦<br />\n當兵咁"},{"pid":"94d226c0c4ae5b9e5fa8e0f60de0636a6d595792","tid":1674380,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有依日"},{"pid":"aa64c3cde1742ef508a3a766330f05547f26f6b5","tid":1674380,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"憑咩<img src=\