核可以=文試搵大專院校，武搵體育學院。見broad 就 其他警區既三粒花，檢控官，新。廉記，同其他紀律部隊。<br />\n<br />\n3年考核完就要轉警區，防止手足情義嘅包庇行為。<br />\n<br />\n重組popo, 廉記,同成立一個有實權 監察&amp;制衡警隊既角色，要同時進行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8745a46e3e4145b2fd9eca0aab0dabc79bbd68","tid":1674380,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a9b6c1edac5045b0673ca88f936b9168f98c0f","tid":1674380,"uid":262522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558b62b8d8ba93316081e65d8a0b4cf802feab4f","tid":1674380,"uid":248131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e7ea6a7342b410693cd2e0acc64052356e3fc2b","tid":1674380,"uid":262522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"香港不需要咁多PoPo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得需要軍隊，起碼體能都好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"香港男女都可當兵<br />\n以色列咁<br />\n港女好勇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"當兵個時期長好多嘛，有啲國家係長徵服兵役，但唔係強制解除兵役"},{"pid":"7d9babf890681a9d4f2030bd45f06cfa4d7cf85e","tid":1674380,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ad19c2b2663e0d5dad1cbe129d457d090553e7","tid":1674380,"uid":262522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a6e9030fabc7fc9d7432e6b9c140664aa40513","tid":1674380,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"冇可能 請唔到人架<br />\n應該由真普選出黎既立法會議員組成有權力罷免及懲處警犬既獨立委員會 每隻狗要每一年進行品德及行為檢查"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"高啲人工？<br />\n每隻check有實行問題<br />\n一年先三百日<br />\n獨立委員會又只係兼職<br />\n做唔哂<br />\n或好那西"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"其實可以考慮獨立委員會再委任全職職員搜集資料?<br />\n再由立會委員根據資料判定?"},{"pid":"bf8a72799e24625eddc20832cd8dc95de1a4531c","tid":1674380,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d9babf890681a9d4f2030bd45f06cfa4d7cf85e","tid":1674380,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ad19c2b2663e0d5dad1cbe129d457d090553e7","t